         <p>
<hi rend="bold">Easter Day, March 31</hi><hi rend="bold superscript underline">st</hi><hi rend="bold">, 1907.</hi>
         </p>
         <p>A most glorious day, but most of the faithful keeping the feast at the sea&#8211;side, or in the country. Communicants the fewest on record.</p>
