         <p>Just 20 less than last year, &amp; that was a bad year!</p>
         <p><persName xml:id="554">Gilbert Simpson</persName> &amp; <persName xml:id="826">Ernest Bennett</persName> came to lunch, and walked with me to the Times Office.</p>
         <p>There was a large congregation at Evensong. We sang the Te Deum, after the Benediction.</p>
         <p>
<hi rend="bold underline"><persName xml:id="55">Knox</persName> &amp; <persName xml:id="1180" display="no">his wife</persName> &amp; <persName xml:id="1448" display="no">daughter</persName> came in to supper</hi>.</p>
         <p>
<hi rend="bold">[197]</hi>
         </p>
